    "description": "<p>A young witch still learning the hinterland secrets and arcana. Can summon flame and curses and break enemy carapaces.</p>",
    "attacks": "<p><strong>Inflict Violence: Incantation.</strong> <strong>Attack a fighter in range 4 with your Faith,</strong> ignoring line of sight, then mark the target until the end of the Arcanist's next riff. While marked, they suffer -1 to all Defenses.</p><p><strong>Gambits</strong> [[/r d6]]</p><p><strong>1-2:</strong> Rush to a better position &gt; <strong>Summon Flame [2]:</strong> Summon a burning flame to <strong>attack an area (range 3 burst 1) with Faith,</strong> setting aflame.</p><p><strong>3-4:</strong> Rush &gt; Inflict Violence &gt; Rush</p><p><strong>5:</strong> Rush &gt; Inflict Violence &gt; <strong>Utterance [1]:</strong> Slide 2 all enemies in blast 5.</p><p><strong>6:</strong> Rush &gt; <strong>Insect Swarm [2]:</strong> Attack an area (range 3 blast 4) with Faith, <strong>debilitating</strong> and <strong>slowing</strong> all enemies hit.</p>",
